strapiSongs.description: This doom metal song depicts a feeling of terror and a reflective period that is experienced in its wake. It is named after the exquisite composer [Edvard Grieg](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Funeral_March_in_Memory_of_Rikard_Nordraak).
